name: CSS Jokes
tagline: Politically incorrect code (all tongue in cheek!)
body:
Ever had a cheeky thought when writing code or observed some unexpected innuendo in someone else's?

This is where CSS Jokes come in.

Sharing some tongue-in-cheek references from our favourite presentational language.

Another side project from [Si](https://twitter.com/Si)
